Package com.orders.cabinet.mapper

Interface AdminMapper

public interface AdminMapper
Mapper interface for converting between Admin and AdminDTO.

This interface defines methods for mapping properties between the Admin entity and the AdminDTO data transfer object. The mappings are handled by MapStruct, a code generation tool for bean mapping.

It provides a single instance of the mapper through the Mappers.getMapper(Class) method. This is a standard approach in MapStruct to create a singleton instance of the mapper.
